						</mml:msub>
					</mml:mfenced>
				</mml:math>
			</inlineequation>, represent either source or destination factors. All scale factors have range <inlineequation>
				<mml:math>
					<mml:mfenced open="[" close="]">
						<mml:mn>0</mml:mn>
						<mml:mn>1</mml:mn>
					</mml:mfenced>
				</mml:math>
			</inlineequation>.
